Computes MOMF

Source: R/cell_deconvolution.R
computeMOMF.Rd

Computes MOMF

Usage

computeMOMF(TPM_matrix, sc_object, signature_file, name_signature)

Arguments

TPM_matrix

A matrix with TPM normalized counts (genes symbols as rows and samples as columns).

sc_object

A matrix with the counts from scRNAseq object (genes as rows and cells as columns)

signature_file

The signature file to use.

name_signature

Signature name to set for the deconvolution results.

Value

A matrix with cell abundance deconvolve with MOMF
